Zm_old_abandoned_v3

old_abandoned was one of the first zm maps that i released and that was 2 years ago, old_abandoned_v3 is totally remade from scratch. The map has a few new additions and has been balanced more for a more even fight. the teleport system from the older versions has been removed and now has just a normal spawn.

  features 

- 2 secrets
- 3d skybox
- cubemaps
